HEADWORD: Limmer
<hw>Lim"mer</hw> <pr>(l⟦icr⟧m"m⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Limber.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Holland.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
